title: 117: Week 1 Review & Who is the best player in the NFL?
itunes:title: 117: Week 1 Review & Who is the best player in the NFL?
description:
Former NFL scouts Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks debate who is the best player in the league. The guys then break down all of the Week 1 action including the Steelers dominant offensive performance and the agelessness of Larry Fitzgerald.
